OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FThe Stormont Assembly has passed the
OL,7,Flong-awaited Sign Language Bill.
OL,9,FMany people from the deaf community
OL,10,Ftravelled to Belfast to witness the
OL,11,Fhistoric moment and cheered the
OL,12,Fpassing of the Bill on the front steps
OL,13,Fof Parliament Buildings.
OL,15,FThe legislation recognises and
OL,16,Fpromotes both British Sign Language
OL,17,Fand Irish Sign Language .
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
