OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FIt places duties on public bodies to
OL,7,Ftake reasonable steps to ensure that
OL,8,Fthe information and services they
OL,9,Fprovide are fully accessible.
OL,11,FThis will include ensuring the
OL,12,Fprovision of free sign language
OL,13,Fclasses to deaf children and their
OL,14,Ffamilies.
OL,16,FThe Bill was passed unanimously by
OL,17,FMLAs on Tuesday afternoon to applause
OL,18,Ffrom the public gallery.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
