PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FIntroducing the final stage of the
OL,7,FBill, Communities Minister Gordon
OL,8,FLyons began his speech in sign
OL,9,Flanguage directed towards the public
OL,10,Fgallery.
OL,12,FHe was met with applause as he hailed
OL,13,Fa historic moment that had been a
OL,14,F"long time coming", adding he could
OL,15,Fnot remember seeing so many people in
OL,16,Fthe gallery for the final stage of any
OL,17,Fother piece of legislation.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,F"I am absolutely delighted at such a
OL,7,Fstrong turnout that we have here
OL,8,Ftoday, and I think that that speaks to
OL,9,Fthe importance of this legislation for
OL,10,Fthe community represented here today,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,FHe went on: "I know that this is a day
OL,14,Fthat has been much anticipated by the
OL,15,Fdeaf and deaf-blind signing community,
OL,16,Ffor them and for the whole of our
OL,17,Fsociety in Northern Ireland, this is a
OL,18,Fday that truly merits being described
OL,19,Fas historic.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]uD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,F"For generations, deaf people have
OL,7,Fbuilt rich linguistic, cultural and
OL,8,Fsocial communities through sign
OL,9,Flanguage, yet that history has too
OL,10,Foften been marked by exclusion; legal
OL,11,Frecognition of sign languages has
OL,12,Flagged far behind lived reality."
OL,14,FChairman of the Stormont Communities
OL,15,FCommittee Colm Gildernew described a
OL,16,F"significant and long-awaited moment".
OL,18,F"I want to say to the community, we
OL,19,Fsee you, hear you, and we will
OL,20,Fcontinue to work on your behalf," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@aO]xD@AOUxD@eO]zD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FHe said this moment carries "both
OL,7,Fopportunity and responsibility", and
OL,8,Femphasised that recognition alone "is
OL,9,Fnot sufficient".
OL,11,F"The legislation must lead to tangible
OL,12,Fimprovements in access to services,
OL,13,Finformation, education and
OL,14,Ffundamentally, participation in public
OL,15,Flife that we all take for granted," he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@_O]pD@cOUqD@OO]sD@AOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,F"This Bill represents a step forward.
OL,7,FIt's not the final destination, and
OL,8,Fits success will ultimately be judged
OL,9,Fnot by the words on the page, but by
OL,10,Fthe lived experience of the people,
OL,11,Fsign language users who are with us
OL,12,Fhere today as we go forward."
OL,14,FSpeaking outside the chamber, Rebecca
OL,15,FMansell, the chief executive of the
OL,16,FBritish Deaf Association, said the
OL,17,Flegislation is crucial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FShe said access to sign language
OL,7,Feducation will make a huge impact for
OL,8,Ffamilies, as well as improve
OL,9,Femployment opportunities.
OL,11,F"Today is such an exciting day for the
OL,12,Fdeaf community, we have been working
OL,13,Fon this Bill for such a long time,
OL,14,Fover 20 years and today we have got
OL,15,Fthe chance for legislation for two
OL,16,Fsign languages, British sign language
OL,17,Fand Irish sign language so it's a
OL,18,Freally crucial day for the deaf
OL,19,Fcommunity in Northern Ireland," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777479067
OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,F"At some point I thought we might not
OL,7,Fget here, but we're here now and I
OL,8,Fthink that's why it's so crucial to
OL,9,Fget the legislation through ` and
OL,10,Fafter that, the hard work starts, just
OL,11,Fto make sure it has meaningful
OL,12,Fimplementation for the deaf community."
OL,14,FThe Bill is set to proceed to Royal
OL,15,FAssent and can then be implemented.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]
