OL,3,C'Crucial day for deaf community' as
OL,4,Clong-awaited Sign Language Bill passed
OL,6,FThe Department for Communities said
OL,7,Fwork was continuing on statutory
OL,8,Fguidance, engagement with the deaf
OL,9,Fcommunity and arrangements to support
OL,10,Fpublic bodies in meeting their new
OL,11,Fresponsibilities.
